trans-unit.source: Provides data for the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.TypeValidationCompleted"></xref> event.
trans-unit.target: Gir dataene for den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.TypeValidationCompleted"> </xref> hendelsen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.TypeValidationCompleted> event occurs when a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox> control performs optional type validation.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.TypeValidationCompleted>hendelsen oppstår når en <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox>kontrollen utfører valgfrie typen validering.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.TypeValidationCompleted>

trans-unit.source: Type validation occurs only when the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.ValidatingType%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property is not `null` and a causal action occurs, such as the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox> control losing focus.
trans-unit.target: Validering av type forekommer bare når den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.ValidatingType%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen er ikke `null` og en causal handlingen utføres, for eksempel den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox>kontrollen å miste fokus.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.ValidatingType%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: *Type validation* is the ability to convert the formatted input string to the type represented by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.ValidatingType%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: *Skriv inn validering* er muligheten til å konvertere formatert Inndatastrengen til typen som representerer den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.ValidatingType%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.ValidatingType%2A>

trans-unit.source: For more information about the type validation process, see the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.TypeValidationCompleted> event.
trans-unit.target: Du finner mer informasjon om typen valideringen av <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.TypeValidationCompleted>hendelsen.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.TypeValidationCompleted>

trans-unit.source: If an event handler is implemented for <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.TypeValidationCompleted>, the handler receives a parameter of type TypeValidationEventArgs.
trans-unit.target: Hvis en hendelsesbehandling implementeres <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.TypeValidationCompleted>, behandlingsprogrammet mottar en parameter av typen TypeValidationEventArgs.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.TypeValidationCompleted>

trans-unit.source: This parameter contains information about the event, such as whether the type conversion process succeeded, the validating type, and so on.
trans-unit.target: Denne parameteren inneholder informasjon om hendelsen, for eksempel om typen konverteringen var vellykket, validering type og så videre.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TypeValidationEventArgs"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TypeValidationEventArgs"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The parameters to the TypeValidationEventArgs constructor are used to initialize the corresponding read-only properties of this class.
trans-unit.target: Parameterne TypeValidationEventArgs-konstruktøren brukes til å initialisere de tilsvarende skrivebeskyttet egenskapene for denne klassen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Type> that the formatted input string was being validated against.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Type>som formatert Inndatastrengen ble valideres mot.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Boolean> value indicating whether the formatted string was successfully converted to the validating type.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Boolean>verdi som angir om den formaterte strengen ble ble konvertert til typen validering.</xref:System.Boolean>

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Object> that is the result of the formatted string being converted to the target type.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Object>som er resultatet av den formaterte strengen konvertert til måltypen.</xref:System.Object>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> containing a description of the conversion process.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.String>som inneholder en beskrivelse av konverteringen.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value indicating whether the event should be canceled.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om hendelsen bør avbrytes.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.TypeValidationCompleted> event occurs just before the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Validating> event.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.TypeValidationCompleted>inntreffer like før den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Validating>hendelsen.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Validating> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.TypeValidationCompleted>

trans-unit.source: Setting the Cancel property to `true` in the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.TypeValidationCompleted> event handler will cancel the event, causing the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox> control to retain focus, unless the subsequent <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Validating> event sets its version of the <xref:System.ComponentModel.CancelEventArgs.Cancel%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property to `false`.
trans-unit.target: Angivelse av Avbryt-egenskapen `true` i den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.TypeValidationCompleted>hendelsesbehandlingen avbrytes hendelsen, fører til at den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox>kontrollen å beholde fokus, med mindre de etterfølgende <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Validating>hendelsen angir versjonen av den <xref:System.ComponentModel.CancelEventArgs.Cancel%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen `false`.</xref:System.ComponentModel.CancelEventArgs.Cancel%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Validating> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.TypeValidationCompleted>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the event should be canceled and focus retained by the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox"></xref> control; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> to continue validation processing.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis hendelsen bør avbrytes og fokus beholdes av den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox"> </xref> kontrollere; ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> fortsette validering behandling.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether the formatted input string was successfully converted to the validating type.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om formatert Inndatastrengen ble ble konvertert til typen validering.

trans-unit.source: The IsValidInput property indicates the success of the `Parse` method found in the <xref:System.Type> represented by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TypeValidationEventArgs.ValidatingType%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen IsValidInput angir hvor vellykket den `Parse` metoden funnet i den <xref:System.Type>representert av den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TypeValidationEventArgs.ValidatingType%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.TypeValidationEventArgs.ValidatingType%2A> </xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: This type must contain `Parse` method(s) having one or both of the following signatures: `public static Object Parse(string)` `public static Object Parse(string, IFormatProvider)` `Parse` is called before the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox> control raises the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.TypeValidationCompleted> event.
trans-unit.target: Denne typen må inneholde `Parse` metode(r) har en eller begge av følgende signaturer: `public static Object Parse(string)` `public static Object Parse(string, IFormatProvider)` `Parse` kalles før den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox>kontrollere hever den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.TypeValidationCompleted>hendelsen.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.TypeValidationCompleted> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox>

trans-unit.source: This method is invoked with the contents, minus the prompt characters, of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.Text%2A> property of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox> class.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden aktiveres med innholdet, minus spør tegnene for <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.Text%2A>egenskapen for <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox>klassen.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.Text%2A>

trans-unit.source: If successful, it returns the converted object; otherwise, it returns `null`.
trans-unit.target: Hvis det er fullført, returneres det konverterte objektet. Ellers returneres `null`.

trans-unit.source: For more information about the type validation process, see the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.TypeValidationCompleted> event.
trans-unit.target: Du finner mer informasjon om typen valideringen av <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.TypeValidationCompleted>hendelsen.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.TypeValidationCompleted>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the formatted input string can be converted into the type specified by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TypeValidationEventArgs.ValidatingType*> property; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis formatert inndata strengen kan konverteres til typen som er angitt av den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TypeValidationEventArgs.ValidatingType*>egenskapen; ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.TypeValidationEventArgs.ValidatingType*>

trans-unit.source: Gets a text message describing the conversion process.
trans-unit.target: Henter en tekstmelding som beskriver konverteringen.

trans-unit.source: The validation process entails converting the formatted user input to the type defined by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.ValidatingType%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Valideringen medfører konvertering formatert brukerinndataene til typen som er definert av den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.ValidatingType%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.ValidatingType%2A>

trans-unit.source: The Message property contains a text description of the conversion process.
trans-unit.target: Meldingsegenskapen inneholder en beskrivelse av konverteringen.

trans-unit.source: Message is primarily useful when conversion fails, as indicated by an <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TypeValidationEventArgs.IsValidInput%2A> property value of `false`.
trans-unit.target: Meldingen er spesielt nyttig når konvertering mislykkes, som angitt av en <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TypeValidationEventArgs.IsValidInput%2A>egenskapsverdi for `false`.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.TypeValidationEventArgs.IsValidInput%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> containing a description of the conversion process.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.String>som inneholder en beskrivelse av konverteringen.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Gets the object that results from the conversion of the formatted input string.
trans-unit.target: Henter objektet som er et resultat av konvertering av formatert Inndatastrengen.

trans-unit.source: The type validation process attempts to convert the formatted input string, not including prompt characters, to the type specified by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TypeValidationEventArgs.ValidatingType%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Typen valideringen forsøker å konvertere formatert Inndatastrengen inkludert ikke spør tegn til typen som er angitt av den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TypeValidationEventArgs.ValidatingType%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.TypeValidationEventArgs.ValidatingType%2A>

trans-unit.source: The ReturnValue property represents the result of the conversion attempt, and is equivalent to the value returned by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.ValidateText%2A> method of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox> class.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen ReturnValue representerer resultatet av forsøk på konvertering og tilsvarer verdien som ble returnert av <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.ValidateText%2A>metoden for <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox>klasse.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.ValidateText%2A>

trans-unit.source: If the validation is successful, an <xref:System.Object> that represents the converted type; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis valideringen var vellykket, en <xref:System.Object>som representerer konverterte typen; ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>.</xref:System.Object>

trans-unit.source: Gets the type that the formatted input string is being validated against.
trans-unit.target: Henter typen formatert Inndatastrengen valideres mot.

trans-unit.source: The validation process only occurs if <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.ValidatingType%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox> class is not `null`.
trans-unit.target: Valideringen oppstår bare hvis <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.ValidatingType%2A?displayProperty=fullName>for den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox>klassen er ikke `null`.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.ValidatingType%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The ValidatingType property references the same type, which represents the target type of the conversion process.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen ValidatingType refererer til den samme typen som representerer måltypen for konverteringen.

trans-unit.source: The target <xref:System.Type> of the conversion process.
trans-unit.target: Målet <xref:System.Type>for konverteringen.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: This should never be <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Dette skal aldri <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>.
